## Operator review checklist before send

(Adapt per scenario — these are the universal checks)

- [ ] Recipient email correct
- [ ] Subject follows `references/subject-line-conventions.md`
- [ ] Opening references prior context, not generic warmth
- [ ] All `{{PLACEHOLDER}}` tokens replaced
- [ ] Sign-off matches recipient relationship
- [ ] Signature block present (drop for internal)
- [ ] Length within scenario norms (60–250 words)
- [ ] No confidential content
- [ ] AIMS routing respected if ME customer

